，不過人地去英美名校讀左6/7/8年洗左球幾兩球囉</blockquote><br />\n其實係你窮先要成日計住計住啫<br />\n有幾可有人要咁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec628e1b7f68b067cf3371b4a14dbe59ff97c66","tid":480634,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T11:44:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>識人HD畢業<br />\n而家返緊茶記 做到成隻狗咁得12K<br />\n<br />\n識人PHD畢業<br />\n係大學教緊書 52K</blockquote><br />\n發夢啦，最好彩果d做到lecturer都係唔知有冇4萬一個月，仲要年年續約；<br />\n係有phd做到assistant prof既，不過人地去英美名校讀左6/7/8年洗左球幾兩球囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nassistant prof人工多過lecturer幾多?"},{"pid":"e69d24fde02068526b8dcd48d14620f777d48b94","tid":480634,"uid":68728,"like":6,"dislike":15,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T11:52:00.000Z","msg":"工程狗有幾多個可以30K啊 ? <br />\n<br />\nbachelor 睪業既去大公司做grad e 都好難5年30k啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e28f56a0233aa622015bb13f1378c86cee81e8","tid":480634,"uid":72608,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T11:53:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>工程狗有幾多個可以30K啊 ? <br />\n<br />\nbachelor 睪業既去大公司做grad e 都好難5年30k啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nching而家搵緊幾多K?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee688746494fcf0fec16cd2d07e941afddad729","tid":480634,"uid":20592,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T12:01:47.000Z","msg":"工程BOY日日帶老母返工 工時長人工低<br />\n又要識文又要識武 有幾多職業係要玩雙修?<br />\n朝早行地盤夜晚返上寫字樓做文件<br />\n壓力大到傻 <br />\n<br />\n得果20K 仲要6日FULLDAY 地盤起貨早8晚8 星期日都要返埋<br />\n又要半工讀讀返個DEGEEEE先有得升<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHEHE 好? 邊到好? 計返工時50$個鐘仲低迵我出黎做炒散"},{"pid":"fcaa9aaa8b02736f0c569182676f6fd0c3b1be6e","tid":480634,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T12:15:31.000Z","msg":"香港就係咁反智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67dc6f35c4415be3d03f1d06196ba526a8166f75","tid":480634,"uid":43964,"like":2,"dislike":